                           мю с Т-образной и с Y-образной средней частью. Лигатура омикрон-ипсилон.</seg>
                        <seg xml:lang="en">Lapidary. Alphas with loop, slanting crossbar, and capping horizontal bar
                           pointing left; mu with T-shaped and Y-shaped middle. Ligature: omicron-upsilon.</seg>
